#{150}{}{I'll see what I can do.}
{150}{}{我看看我能做什么。 -- I'll see what I can do.}
#{151}{}{How much longer will the generator last, if we fix it?}
{151}{}{如果我们把发电机修好，它还能用多久？ -- How much longer will the generator last, if we fix it?}
#{152}{}{We have a little needs - light, heating, kitchen utilities. We would have enough stored energy to last our families at least ten years.}
{152}{}{我们有一点需要-光，暖气，厨房公用设施。我们将有足够的储存能量维持我们的家庭至少十年。 -- We have a little needs - light, heating, kitchen utilities. We would have enough stored energy to last our families at least ten years.}
#{153}{}{I see you have managed to fix electricity! Thank you. You really helped us. I do not know how to repay you. Here, take this whiskey. I found it in an old house and kept in case of a holiday. But it is better to share it with a good person.}
{153}{}{我看你已经修好了电！非常感谢。你真的帮了我们。我不知道如何报答你。来，拿着威士忌。我在一所旧房子里找到的，留着以防万一。但最好和一个好人分享。 -- I see you have managed to fix electricity! Thank you. You really helped us. I do not know how to repay you. Here, take this whiskey. I found it in an old house and kept in case of a holiday. But it is better to share it with a good person.}
#{154}{}{Always welcome.}
{154}{}{永远欢迎。 -- Always welcome.}
